Jericho.

Ephrain: Ephrain, or Ephron, a city of Benjamin, is placed by Eusebius,
eight miles north of Jerusalem, near Bethel. Josephus calls Ephrain and
Bethel two little cities; and places the former in the tribe of
Benjamin, near the wilderness of Judea, in the way to Jericho. [Ch2
15:8](../../../bib/kjv/ch2015.htm#008.md); [Jos
